TI  - A conceptual framework for enhancing the utility of rainfall hazard forecasts for agriculture in marginal environments
T2  - NATURAL HAZARDS
LA  - English
KW  - drought definition
KW  - drought indicators
KW  - seasonal rainfall forecasts
KW  - climate forecast utility
KW  - agricultural applications
KW  - conceptual framework
