TI  - Climate and land use change driving divergent surface water dynamics in the Northern China agro-pastoral ecotone
T2  - JOURNAL OF HYDROLOGY-REGIONAL STUDIES
LA  - English
KW  - Surface water depletion
KW  - Net water yield
KW  - Irrigation efficiency paradox
