TI  - Crop-livestock integration provides opportunities to mitigate environmental trade-offs in transitioning smallholder agricultural systems of the Greater Mekong Subregion
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Agricultural diversity
KW  - Greenhouse gas emissions
