TI  - Combined application of the EM-DEA and EX-ACT approaches for integrated assessment of resource use efficiency, sustainability and carbon footprint of smallholder maize production practices in sub-Saharan Africa
T2  - JOURNAL OF CLEANER PRODUCTION
LA  - English
