TI  - Pre-Qin Period Settlement Development in the Li River Basin in China: Environmental Factors and Predictive Modeling
T2  - QUATERNARY INTERNATIONAL
LA  - English
KW  - Li River Basin
KW  - Pre-Qin Period in China
KW  - Settlement Archaeology
