TI  - A sustainable agricultural development assessment method and a case study in China based on euclidean distance theory
T2  - JOURNAL OF CLEANER PRODUCTION
LA  - English
KW  - Sustainability of agricultural development method
KW  - Euclidean distance theory
KW  - Goal system
KW  - Zero system
KW  - INDICATORS
