TI  - Evaluation of future climate using SDSM and secondary data (TRMM and NCEP) for poorly gauged catchments of Uganda: the case of Aswa catchment
T2  - THEORETICAL AND APPLIED CLIMATOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - REANALYSIS DATASETS
KW  - DAILY RAINFALL
KW  - ERA-INTERIM
KW  - TEMPERATURE
