TI  - Silvopastoral systems for offsetting livestock emissions in the tropics: a case study of a dairy farm in Costa Rica
T2  - AGRONOMY FOR SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Life cycle assessment
KW  - Carbon sequestration
