TI  - Situational analyses on cowpea value chain in Zambia: the case of an untapped legume
T2  - COGENT FOOD & AGRICULTURE
LA  - English
KW  - crop diversity
KW  - seed development
KW  - black-eyed pea
KW  - value chain
KW  - markets
KW  - end-user
KW  - policy
KW  - research
