TI  - Estimating paddy rice yield using PlanetScope imagery and machine learning
T2  - SMART AGRICULTURAL TECHNOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Feature selection
KW  - Machine learning
KW  - Paddy rice
KW  - PlanetScope
