TI  - Monitoring sub-canopy inundation dynamics in global croplands: An unexplored application of SWOT satellite data
T2  - AGRICULTURAL WATER MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Cropland inundation status
KW  - Beneath vegetation
KW  - Year-round dynamics
KW  - Diverse climate zones
