TI  - Effect of moisture management practices and zinc fertilization on growth, productivity and economics of pearl millet (Pennisetum glaucum) under pearl millet-mustard (Brassica juncea) system
T2  - INDIAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL SCIENCES
LA  - English
