TI  - The current fertilizer regimes cause phosphorus deficit in paddy soils and decreased rice phosphorus uptake: a study in Shanghai, China
T2  - LAND DEGRADATION & DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - long-term field study
KW  - non-point source pollution
KW  - organic fertilizer
KW  - phosphorus balance
KW  - Rice
KW  - sustainable agriculture
KW  - RHIZOSPHERE
