TI  - Nitrogen mineralization in sub-tropical paddy soils in relation to soil mineralogy, management, pH, carbon, nitrogen and iron contents
T2  - EUROPEAN JOURNAL OF SOIL SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - ORGANIC-MATTER
