TI  - EFFECTS OF SOIL-APPLIED POTASSIUM ON POTASSIUM USE EFFICIENCY, LEAF WATER, AND BIOCHEMICAL ATTRIBUTES OF COTTON CULTIVARS UNDER REDUCED IRRIGATION
