TI  - Mineral nitrogen dynamics in irrigated rice-wheat system under different irrigation and establishment methods and residue levels in arid drylands of Central Asia
T2  - EUROPEAN JOURNAL OF AGRONOMY
LA  - English
KW  - Dry seeded rice
KW  - Alternate wet and dry irrigation
KW  - N balance
