TI  - Can productivity and profitability be enhanced in intensively managed cereal systems while reducing the environmental footprint of production? Assessing sustainable intensification options in the breadbasket of India
T2  - AGRICULTURE ECOSYSTEMS & ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Sustainable intensification
KW  - Zero-tillage
KW  - Global warming potential
