TI  - Food shopping during the COVID-19 pandemic: an exploratory study in four Near Eastern countries
T2  - JOURNAL OF ISLAMIC MARKETING
LA  - English
KW  - COVID-19
KW  - Food shopping
KW  - Lebanon
KW  - Palestinian territories
KW  - Oman
KW  - Qatar
