TI  - Identifying conflicts and sectoral dynamics prior to marine spatial planning: A case study of Bhola and Hatia, two coastal islands of Bangladesh
T2  - MARINE POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Multiple-use conflicts
KW  - Fisheries management
KW  - Artisanal fisheries
