TI  - Genomic loci associated with grain yield under well-watered and water-stressed conditions in multiple bi-parental maize populations
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - water stress
KW  - maize
KW  - sub-Saharan Africa
