TI  - The role of fish and fisheries in recovering from natural hazards: Lessons learned from Vanuatu
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE & POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Cyclone
KW  - El-Nino
KW  - Coastal fisheries
KW  - Management
KW  - Tropical-Cyclone Pam
KW  - POST-TSUNAMI ACEH
