TI  - Influential Climate Teleconnections for Spatiotemporal Precipitation Variability in the Lancang-Mekong River Basin From 1952 to 2015
T2  - JOURNAL OF GEOPHYSICAL RESEARCH-ATMOSPHERES
LA  - English
