TI  - The mitigating role of climate smart villages to the impacts of COVID-19 pandemic in the Myanmar rural communities
T2  - CURRENT RESEARCH IN ENVIRONMENTAL SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Climate smart village
KW  - Climate smart agriculture
KW  - Myanmar
KW  - Community -based adaptation
