TI  - Quantifying Coastal Vulnerability and the Protective Role of Mangrove Rehabilitation: A GIS-Remote Sensing Analysis From Mojo, Pemalang, Indonesia
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL QUALITY MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - coastal vulnerability index
KW  - geographic information system
